    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stranded With Darkness</strong> is a first person, co-op survival horror game for up to 4 players online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your escape pod gets stranded on a distant desert like planet. You find yourself racing against time. Even though the planet seems mostly dead during the day, its a different story when the sun goes down. You realize you are no longer alone... The habitants of the planet do not like your presence and will do everything they can to silence your call for aid. Defend your radio beacon at all costs and hope someone arrives before its to late to get you and your crew of this forsaken planet...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107810/extras/6413fb46adbd94bc0a87ceba5dc90203.poster.avif?t=1751403118\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107810/extras/6413fb46adbd94bc0a87ceba5dc90203.webm?t=1751403118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107810/extras/6413fb46adbd94bc0a87ceba5dc90203.mp4?t=1751403118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>                    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Included in Early Access version at launch:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 map (Desert Planet)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Materials to build from</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 game mode (Endless Survival with high score)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Monster types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1-4 Online CO-OP</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*More maps and content will be included in future updates.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cooperate:</strong> Stranded With Darkness is a 1-4 player cooperative experience where you must work together to build and defend your only chance of survival. Stay out of the dark, stay close to your crew and make sure you keep breathing long enough to see the sun rise once more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore:</strong> Explore the planet for different materials and to improve your defenses. BUT! Make sure you have enough time to get back before darkness falls. It's easy to get lost and stranded... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107810/extras/737fab8e314ccdd423ea49bfaee1d961.poster.avif?t=1751403118\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107810/extras/737fab8e314ccdd423ea49bfaee1d961.webm?t=1751403118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107810/extras/737fab8e314ccdd423ea49bfaee1d961.mp4?t=1751403118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Base building:</strong> Build a base to defend the beacon, find different ways to make the most out of the material you have. Only traps isn't always the best defense! Test different strategies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107810/extras/9bbd5647070fd9bf481da59c93c89001.poster.avif?t=1751403118\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107810/extras/9bbd5647070fd9bf481da59c93c89001.webm?t=1751403118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107810/extras/9bbd5647070fd9bf481da59c93c89001.mp4?t=1751403118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive or Fail:</strong> There are only two ways out, survive until someone finds your call for aid, or become part of the planet....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107810/extras/1004ea16d29a9dd7325f0d61d98132ab.poster.avif?t=1751403118\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107810/extras/1004ea16d29a9dd7325f0d61d98132ab.webm?t=1751403118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107810/extras/1004ea16d29a9dd7325f0d61d98132ab.mp4?t=1751403118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul>",
